name: James Dean
description:
Fan of James Dean? The unforgettable bad boy of all time?

Drawn by me using black ink.

The postcard is printed on Canon SELPHY Compact Photo Printers using its authentic photo paper.

Other celebrity icons are also available at http://flic.kr/s/aHsjEtRcXG

Happy shopping and shipping is FREE!

name: Ship fighting
description:
Experimentation on using watercolour pencil.

Giclee Print from my original (this is NUMBER 1 as this is my first time to do a giclee print)
Medium (watercolour pencil + a bit of graphite touchings)
Size of the painting (10.5cm x 14cm)
Printed on A5 (14.8cm x 21cm)
P&P (included) on heavy board to avoid bending while posting.
Can sign and date at back as buyers choice

For more please visit http://www.flickr.com/photos/americodasneves/

description:

name: Bibico
description:
BIBICO is the fruit of my self-taught designer's toy made of resin. They are limited to 50 and hand-painted. Few available left.

Euro55/pcs.
